      Prohm becomes like stone - immovable and nearly invincible. While active, 
      enemies who attack him take damage from his sharp back plates.
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 15
    staminaCost: 40
    range: 0
    type: Buff
    element: Earth
    statusEffects:
      - damage_reduction_90
      - reflect_damage_50
