    description: |
      Prohm channels the power of the ancient earth itself. The ground 
      shatters, creating massive fissures that swallow enemies and 
      raise protective stone walls for allies.
    damage: 90
    cooldown: 60
    staminaCost: 80
    range: 15
    type: AoE
    element: Earth
    statusEffects:
      - terrain_destruction
      - ally_stone_walls
      - stun_3s

  _passiveAbility:
    abilityId: prohm_ancient_endurance
    abilityName: Eternal Patience
    description: |
      Prohm has waited millennia. He can wait a bit more. Regenerates health 
      slowly over time, and cannot be killed in one hit - will always 
      survive with 1 HP from a fatal blow (once per battle).
    damage: 0
    cooldown: 0
    staminaCost: 0
    range: 0
    type: Buff
    element: Earth

