  # PERSONALITY
  _personality:
    bravery: 95
    kindness: 90
    wisdom: 100
    humor: 30
    loyalty: 100
    curiosity: 45

  _likes:
    - Children
    - Silence
    - Sunbathing on warm rocks
    - Watching things grow
    - The feeling of rain

  _dislikes:
    - Loud noises
    - Being rushed
    - Those who destroy without purpose
    - Being reminded of loneliness
    - Cold nights

  _favoriteFood: He doesn't need to eat, but he enjoys the company of meals
  _hobby: Watching clouds and counting seasons
  _fear: Outliving everyone again
  _dream: To finally rest, but not before seeing this new family safe

  # VOICE LINES (Prohm speaks rarely and slowly)
  _voiceLines:
    lines:
      - type: Greeting
        text: "..."  # Sometimes silence is greeting enough
      - type: Greeting
        text: "...Friend."
      - type: Selection
        text: "*slow, rumbling nod*"
      - type: Selection
        text: "...I will protect."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "...The earth... remembers."
      - type: BattleStart
        text: "...I stood before the mountains. I can stand before you."
      - type: Attack
        text: "*rumble*"
      - type: Attack
        text: "...Move."
      - type: SpecialAttack
        text: "...Like stone."
      - type: Ultimate
        text: "...THE EARTH... ANSWERS..."
      - type: Hurt
        text: "*ancient groan*"
      - type: LowHealth
        text: "...Not yet..."
      - type: Victory
        text: "...Rest now."
      - type: Victory
        text: "*content rumble*"
      - type: Defeat
        text: "...Finally... rest..."
      - type: LevelUp
        text: "...Still growing... even now."
      - type: Idle
        text: "*watches a beetle crawl by with infinite patience*"
      - type: Idle
        text: "...That cloud... looks like my sister. She would have liked this age."
      - type: Funny
        text: "...Why rush?... I have... *long pause* ...time."
      - type: Funny
        text: "...Kavi asked my age... I started counting... he fell asleep."

  # RELATIONSHIPS
  _relationships:
    - characterId: champa_elephant
      characterName: Champa
      type: Friend
      affinity: 90
      relationshipDescription: |
        Champa and Prohm understand each other without words. Both are gentle 
        giants who carry more than their size suggests. They share comfortable 
        silences.
      specialDialogue:
        - "...She understands."
        - "...Gentle heart... in great body. Like me... once."

    - characterId: kavi_monkey
      characterName: Kavi
      type: Friend
      affinity: 85
      relationshipDescription: |
        Kavi's chaos exhausts Prohm, but the monkey's joy is infectious. Kavi 
        uses Prohm as a jungle gym. Prohm pretends to mind.
      specialDialogue:
        - "...He is very... loud." *allows Kavi to climb on him*
        - "...Like a flea. But... a good flea."

    - characterId: makara_dragon
      characterName: Makara
      type: Friend
      affinity: 75
      relationshipDescription: |
        Two ancient creatures from before recorded history. They share memories 
        of a world long gone. Prohm appreciates warm rocks; Makara provides.
      specialDialogue:
        - "...He cooks. I eat... to be polite. It is... actually good."
        - "...We remember... the same stars."

  # BACKSTORY
  _birthplace: The First Garden (no longer exists)
  _occupation: Temple Guardian / Last Ancient
  _familyBackground: |
    Had a sister, brothers, a whole herd of Ancients. All gone now.
    The temple children have become his new family.
  _backstory: |
    See full biography above.
  _keyMemories:
    - "The day I realized I was the last one. I slept for a century."
    - "A child named Srey who called me 'Grandpa Rock.' She is grown with children now. I watched over all of them."
    - "Moving for the first time in ages to protect the village children. Everything hurt. Everything felt wonderful."
    - "Champa sitting beside me in silence. First time in eons I didn't feel alone."

